</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A1706018002">
<title>
Fuel Level Sensor
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A1706017">Fuel Level Sensor Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Do not touch resister plate (1) and cause deformation of arm (2). It may cause sub fuel level sensor to fail.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101170039.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.718mm" ver = "01" gw = "193" gh = "144"/>
</figure>
</attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that resistance between terminals “a” and “b” of fuel level sensor changes depending on float position.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check resistance between terminals “a” and “b” at each float position in the following table.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace fuel level sensor.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
